<%\nFunction HtmlEncode(input)\n    If Not IsNull(input) Then\n        input = Replace(input, "&", "&amp;")\n        input = Replace(input, "<", "&lt;")\n        input = Replace(input, ">", "&gt;")\n        input = Replace(input, """", "&#34;")\n        input = Replace(input, "'", "&#39;")\n    End If\n    HtmlEncode = input\nEnd Function\n\n' Usage example\nDim userInput\nuserInput = Request.QueryString("name")\nResponse.Write(HtmlEncode(userInput))\n%>